//As soon as dawn breaks, you and Horace are off. Just a few hours later you find yourself in the bustling streets of Purple Town. It reminds you of the annual fair, the masses, colors and shapes. Horace moves confidently through the crowded mainstreet and your heart beats faster as you dismount in front of the  famous Bar Mans Bar & Shag. There are a small number of robotic and organic steeds tied near the entrance of the saloon.//

[["Maybe I should explore more first?" ->MaybeIShould]]

[["Should I tie you to the other steeds?" -> bondageJoke]]

//You give her a little smile.//

I like your hat.


[[Continue. ->AndILikeYours]]

Yeah whatever, I'll show you...

//You mumble and grumble, moving back a little.//

[[Continue. ->ConsidersItAWin]]

//You breath out and turn to look at Horace. He gives you a pretty impressed nod that you know he uses in place of giving thumbs up, what with his lack of thumbs and all.//

Wow, Jessie. I didn't think you had that in you.

[["Thanks Horace." You go inside. ->GoInPumped]]

//You laugh nervously and try to play it off.//

Hah, yeah, of course I knew that! 

[[You feel pretty pumped and go inside with a swagger. ->GoInPumped]]

Oh wow, oh heck, wow...

//You shake a little, realizing how close you came to actually get into a fight with one of the most infamous gunslingers in the eastern Reaches.//

[[Take a moment to gather yourself, before going inside.->GoInside]]

Oh god damn, hecking heck! Why do I let them walk over me like that!

//You feel tears welling up in your eyes.]]

[[Continue. ->HonestHoraceNoFight]]

//She winks again, and moves past you, not without pinching your butt though.//

[[Avoid looking Horace in the eye and go inside.->GoInsideAshamed]]

[["Hecking heck, why did I let her do this to me!" ->HeckingHeck]]

//You get up a little shaky and wipe the spit off your boot, feeling ashamed and humiliated as you do. Horace is coming over, shouting something nasty at the cowgirl who shouts something nasty back. He glances at you and you can see he is worried about you.//

[[Quickly go inside and avoid talking to Horace. ->GoInsideAshamed]]

[[Damnit Horace...->DamnitHorace]]
